{"id": 1470, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在网上做的哪些事情，其实并不想和“社交”扯上关系？", "description": "致那些讨厌的、经常泄露我秘密的 App 们。（题图来自：David J.McMillan）", "record_count": 23086, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170124111510ro7x0jVcO6NXYb81.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-02T17:00:48Z", "questions": [{"id": 1784, "title": "你在网上做的哪些事情，其实并不想和“社交”扯上关系？", "content": "你在网上做的哪些事情，其实并不想和“社交”扯上关系？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 157710, "content": "不希望豆瓣账号被认识的人发现，看的书、电影只和友邻分享", "image": "img/option/option/201701241245542Tmyk1VDKgsPcjO7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 157778, "content": "运动软件也总是提醒关注认识的人，我们还没到肌肉相见的地步吧……", "image": "img/option/option/20170124143010p6sWR2wDzcfho3li.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 157781, "content": "购物和找餐厅的时候总弹出“你的朋友买过/去过”", "image": "img/option/option/20170124143329xX3ScB4W7eDvsV2F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 157782, "content": "用社交网络关联了游戏账号，好友能看到“XX刚刚玩过这个游戏”", "image": "img/option/option/20170124144038U02cFZ87NGAVlPrb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 157783, "content": "朋友圈上给别人回复，此前点过赞的人都能收到提示", "image": "img/option/option/20170124144526cLvGKpFe9o64SDil.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 157784, "content": "知乎微博点个赞都能被关注的人看到", "image": "img/option/option/2017012414473108cqG6U4kK3tM7e9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 157794, "content": "在手机上背了几个单词，完成页面多点了几下竟然分享到朋友圈了", "image": "img/option/option/20170124151359dVMpW9bPTyOn5rKA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}